-\Delta v(x)=\delta_{0}(x) 
v(x)=\frac{1}{4\pi\left|x\right|}
-\Delta v(x)+Av(x)=\delta_{0}(x) 
C_{1}\exp({\sqrt{A}x})+C_{2}\exp({-\sqrt{A}x})
H=(-\Delta+A)
A \geq 0
H\, E=\delta
\Delta \frac{1}{\vert x \vert}=-4\pi \delta
-\Delta-B,\, B \geq 0
E(x)=\frac{\exp(-\sqrt{A} \vert x \vert)}{4 \pi \vert x \vert }
E_{\pm}(x)=\frac{\exp(\pm \mathcal{i}\sqrt{B} \vert x \vert)}{4 \pi \vert x \vert}.
